表格植毛机管理的代码预览

if exists (select 1
from sysobjects
where id = object_id('PlantBristlesMachineInfo')
and type = 'U')
drop table PlantBristlesMachineInfo
go

/*==============================================================*/
/* Table: PlantBristlesMachineInfo */
/*==============================================================*/
create table PlantBristlesMachineInfo (
ID int identity(1,1),
MachineCode varchar(50) collate Chinese_PRC_CI_AS not null,
MachineType varchar(50) collate Chinese_PRC_CI_AS not null,
MachineAxisNum integer collate Chinese_PRC_CI_AS not null,
GroupNum smallint null,
Manufacturers varchar(200) collate Chinese_PRC_CI_AS null,
MakeDate datetime null,
MachineSpace integer not null,
SuitBrush varchar(50) not null,
MachineNumber varchar(50) collate Chinese_PRC_CI_AS null,
MachineUpNo varchar(50) collate Chinese_PRC_CI_AS null,
Power decimal(10, 2) collate Chinese_PRC_CI_AS null,
MaintainDate varchar(50) collate Chinese_PRC_CI_AS null,
MachinePhoto image null,
Remark varchar(200) null,
DispatchCount int null,
constraint PK_MachineSuit primary key ()
WITH (IGNORE_DUP_KEY = OFF) ON [PRIMARY]
)
ON [PRIMARY] TEXTIMAGE_ON [PRIMARY]
go

declare @CurrentUser sysname
select @CurrentUser = user_name()
execute sp_addextendedproperty 'MS_Description',
'3-16中选择',
'user', @CurrentUser, 'table', 'PlantBristlesMachineInfo', 'column', 'MachineAxisNum'
go
